  projects:
    - name: Cafe Roadway
      tag: Flagship Project
      tech: HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript, Bootstrap 5, Canvas API, LocalStorage
      live_link: https://shudanshubora1410.github.io/cafe-roadway
      github_link: https://github.com/shudanshubora1410/cafe-roadway
      highlights:
        - Engineered a premium dark-luxury restaurant website with 43+ interactive
          features using only 3 files (HTML, CSS, JS) — no frameworks used.
        - Built a dynamic Bill Calculator with automated GST computation and
          WhatsApp API integration for seamless order placement.
        - Implemented Dark/Light Mode with LocalStorage persistence, Live Menu
          Search, Spin-the-Wheel discount game, and Canvas-based Confetti animation.
        - Integrated Table Booking system, Order Tracker, Review System,
          Birthday Special, and Happy Hours countdown timer.
        - Added JSON-LD Schema Markup for 100% SEO optimization, Open Graph
          tags, and full mobile responsiveness.
        - Implemented 8 keyboard shortcuts for navigation and custom gold
          cursor with hover effects.

    - name: Homyz
      tag: Incapp IT Training — Final Project
      tech: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Bootstrap 5, AOS, Google Sheets API
      live_link: https://shudanshubora1410.github.io/Homyz
      github_link: https://github.com/shudanshubora1410/Homyz
      highlights:
        - Built a modern real estate platform targeting Delhi NCR covering
          Noida, Gurgaon, Greater Noida, Faridabad and South Delhi.
        - Implemented dynamic property filtering by type (Apartments, Villas,
          Houses, Penthouses) with smooth fade transitions.
        - Integrated Google Sheets API as backend for contact form — stores
          leads directly into spreadsheet without any server required.
        - Added WhatsApp floating button with pre-filled message, Google Maps
          integration, and animated locality explorer section.
        - Built favorites system with heart animation, toast notifications,
          animated counter stats and typed location effect.
        - Fully responsive design with AOS scroll animations, custom
          scrollbar, and mobile-first approach throughout.

    - name: NovaCare — Hospital Management System
      tag: Full-Stack Project — 2nd Year
      tech: Node.js, Express.js, MySQL, JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3
      github_link: https://github.com/shudanshubora1410/hospital-management-system
      highlights:
        - Developed a complete full-stack hospital management system with
          24 RESTful API endpoints covering all CRUD operations.
        - Implemented role-based access control system with 3 distinct
          roles — Admin, Doctor, and Patient — each with separate dashboards.
        - Built automated 18% GST billing system that calculates and generates
          invoices dynamically for each patient visit.
        - Designed real-time statistics dashboard showing patient count,
          appointments, revenue, and doctor availability.
        - Used MySQL for relational database design with normalized tables
          for Patients, Doctors, Appointments, and Billing.

    - name: Email Sender Application
      tag: Java Desktop Project
      tech: Java, Swing, JavaMail API, Gmail SMTP
      github_link: https://github.com/shudanshubora1410/Email-Sender-Java
      highlights:
        - Built a Java Swing desktop application for automated email sending
          using Gmail SMTP protocol.
        - Supports multiple recipients, custom subject lines, message body
          and file attachment functionality.
        - Implemented secure authentication using Gmail App Password with
          TLS encryption for data safety.

    - name: LeetCode Solutions — Java
